  {
    "title": "Snösmältning",
    "year": 2026,
    "category": "Painting",
    "material": "Oil pastel, acrylic and oil on canvas, walnut frame",
    "size": "120 x 80 cm",
    "description": "Snösmältning is a painting that explores the idea of transition and natural processes, as a metaphor for the movements and time passing in the body and mind. The mountainous landscape and paths and their resemblance with our insides. The viewer is invited to reflect on the beauty found in moments of change and the inevitable passage of time.",
